WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.128
The financial transactions are fully, securely, and transparently handled by

00:00:04.128 --> 00:00:08.256
Amazon from start to finish. The customer simply pays for

00:00:08.256 --> 00:00:12.384
our platform through their existing, pre-approved, and pre-negotiated billing framework.

00:00:12.384 --> 00:00:16.512
Once the transaction successfully clears, Amazon gracefully manages all the

00:00:16.512 --> 00:00:20.640
backend financial complexity, collects the global funds, and securely disburses

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:24.768
the final payment directly to AppsFlyer.
